summary: Body Texture for CoverKhajiits by mrLenski
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i17.photobucket.com/albums/b74/Desert-Rat/Skyrim%20Mods/Bannerfemalesmall.jpg[/IMG]

[b]Hi everyone[/b]

This is a High Detail texture fitting for the Khajiit Face texture made by mrLenski.
After request i did the female Version too.
This Mod contains just the Body textures! You will need to download the Textures for the head too. Link is posted below.

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6192]Also the Male Version is available here[/url]

[b]What is this Mod?[/b]

This mod replaces the Vanilla Body texture with a high detail body, which fits to the Face Texture of the CoverKhajiits mod. 


[b]What else do i need?[/b]

I recommend you to download mrLenskis [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5941]coverkhajiits[/url]


[b]How to install?[/b]

Just copy the texture Folder into your Skyrim/Data Folder.


[b]How to uninstall this?[/b]

Simply by deleting the Khajiitfemale folder out of your \"textures/character/actors/\" Folder.... 


[b]Credits[/b]

You can upload the File on other Sites aslong you name me as creator of the Mod.
Also you can add this to your own Mod, just give some credits for the work.

Thanks to Behtesda for this cool Game!

If you have made Screenshots, feel free to post them here, so other People see how they look, also i am really interrested in your Character.

I hope you enjoy my Mods!

Have fun,
JazzJR

[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/modules/members/index.php?id=2741960]Take a look at my other Mods.[/url]
Thanks for your time. Feel free to comment if you like my Mod or if you found any bugs, or things to improve.


[IMG]http://i17.photobucket.com/albums/b74/Desert-Rat/Banner.jpg[/IMG]
